1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 14=

3
00:00:12,119 --> 00:00:15,199
Hmph. You think taking me down means

4
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:19,079
Qiao Nian can just take over Qiao Group?

5
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:21,079
Hmph. No.

6
00:00:21,719 --> 00:00:23,679
She doesn't even qualify.

7
00:00:24,399 --> 00:00:26,719
She isn't even from the Qiao bloodline.

8
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:30,039
What? How's that possible?

9
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:32,200
Is that true?

10
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,759
What proof do you have to claim that?

11
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:36,320
And what proof do you have
to claim she is?

12
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,000
I can prove it.

13
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:43,719
Mr. Qiao?

14
00:00:44,719 --> 00:00:45,840
Dad?

15
00:00:47,159 --> 00:00:47,960
Grandpa?

16
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,119
He is still alive!

17
00:00:49,479 --> 00:00:50,479
He's back!

18
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:51,399
Look.

19
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,479
Grandpa.

20
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,960
Grandpa!

21
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:58,200
Are you okay?

22
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:00,039
I'm fine, Grandpa.

23
00:01:00,359 --> 00:01:01,479
That's good.

24
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,079
That's good.

25
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:04,719
Grandpa!

26
00:01:05,079 --> 00:01:06,200
Dad is alive?

27
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,519
(It's all over now.)

28
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:09,319
Grandpa!

29
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:18,120
What exactly happened?

30
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,400
The day of the fire,

31
00:01:19,519 --> 00:01:22,040
I broke into the cellar
through the window

32
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,000
and found Mr. Qiao.

33
00:01:23,239 --> 00:01:24,480
I saved him.

34
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,239
He was in and out of consciousness

35
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:28,400
after that,

36
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:32,920
but he told me not
to tell anyone he was alive.

37
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,480
Why?

38
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,239
He wanted to see
what Qiao Wenjun would do next.

39
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:41,480
He also asked me
to protect you from the shadows.

40
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:44,560
(He's so weak,)

41
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,959
(but he's still protecting me.)

42
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,800
(Dad,)

43
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,479
(don't blame me.)

44
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,439
(Dad,)

45
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:48,800
(I'll make it up
to you in my next life.)

46
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,919
Wenjun.

47
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:59,199
How did you recognize me?

48
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,439
Come on.

49
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:05,840
How could a father
not recognize his own daughter?

50
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:09,400
So you still see me as your daughter?

51
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,439
Of course.

52
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:14,080
Zhenxuan actually came

53
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,000
to see me earlier.

54
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,800
Dad,

55
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,759
how can you just hand Wenjun's work

56
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:20,680
over to me?

57
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,120
That's not fair to her.

58
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:26,599
This project has to be yours.

59
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:29,199
She can't handle Jiang Xiao.

60
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:32,479
I don't think she is
worse than him in business.

61
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:36,280
What about turning on people
after using them?

62
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,879
What about being ruthless?

63
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,759
Wenjun is too simple.

64
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,400
She doesn't think ahead.

65
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,360
Jiang Xiao could easily use her.

66
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:51,960
This investment from Jiang Group

67
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,919
looks like help, but it's a trap.

68
00:03:56,840 --> 00:04:00,560
He wants control
of the whole Qiao Group through it.

69
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,159
You may not want to be involved,

70
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,520
but you understand people.

71
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,560
You can see the logic
behind the problem.

72
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,960
The company needs that.

73
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:15,000
If you want to protect Wenjun,

74
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:17,600
you have to keep Jiang Xiao in check.

75
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,600
I was stubborn.

76
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,680
I thought I was taking care of you,

77
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:31,800
but I made you feel ignored.

78
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,680
My children...

79
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:42,480
I failed as a father.

80
00:04:44,199 --> 00:04:45,279
I'm sorry.

81
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,160
I'm sorry.

82
00:04:48,839 --> 00:04:51,000
What's the point of saying that now?

83
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:55,000
After Zhenxuan was gone,

84
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:58,680
why didn't you care about me more?

85
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,560
You were obsessed with finding him.

86
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:05,480
You knew he wouldn't
come back the way you wanted.

87
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:11,000
I know my stubbornness

88
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:13,000
hurt you both.

89
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:18,680
It wasn't until I faced life and death

90
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,079
that I realized

91
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:25,319
you both have your own lives.

92
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,639
Dad,

93
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:36,000
I'm just glad you're alive.

94
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,240
I regret it.

95
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:42,759
I regret everything I did.

96
00:05:43,319 --> 00:05:44,759
Can you forgive me?

97
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:46,560
Yes.

98
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,480
Dad.

99
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,240
Yes.

100
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,199
Dad,

101
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:55,040
I just wanted your love.

102
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,279
I know.

103
00:05:59,759 --> 00:06:01,839
I know.

104
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,920
I know.

105
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,920
Grandpa, you're awake.

106
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,959
What are you doing here?

107
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,040
I just came to see him.

108
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,480
Nian,

109
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,399
I asked her to come.

110
00:06:30,079 --> 00:06:31,759
Why is she here with a syringe?

111
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,800
Nian.

112
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,040
Grandpa.

113
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,560
Let her go.

114
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:41,360
Dad, I'll go now.

115
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,600
Grandpa.

116
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,319
Grandpa,

117
00:06:57,759 --> 00:06:58,759
how are you feeling?

118
00:06:58,839 --> 00:07:00,120
Any discomfort?

119
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:03,759
Nian, I'm fine.

120
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,920
I just want to rest.

121
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,240
Okay.

122
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:24,399
(I don't even have
the face to see them anymore.)

123
00:07:29,020 --> 00:07:32,460
(Inheritance Donation Agreement)

124
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:41,199
Hello?

125
00:07:41,639 --> 00:07:42,560
Mom!

126
00:07:42,759 --> 00:07:43,839
Mom, I was wrong!

127
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,199
Please,

128
00:07:45,199 --> 00:07:46,680
get me out of here!

129
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,319
Alright.

130
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:51,120
Mom, I'll do whatever you say!

131
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,399
I'll listen!

132
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,360
Mom!

133
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:54,759
Yiran...

134
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,160
Mom.

135
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,759
I left you some money.

136
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,360
From now on,

137
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:03,720
you're on your own.

138
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:05,560
Mom?

139
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,439
No matter

140
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:11,680
what happens, don't rush in blindly.

141
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,920
Stay calm.

142
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,959
Mom,

143
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,920
what happened?

144
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,120
You sound so strange.

145
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,439
It's nothing.

146
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:24,000
I'm just tired.

147
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:26,160
I need to rest.

148
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:28,319
Mom, what's wrong?

149
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,319
Talk to me!

150
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,800
Mom, say something!

151
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:33,679
Please say something!

152
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,240
Mom!

153
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,360
Doctor, how is he?

154
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:38,759
He's fine.

155
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:39,879
He just needs rest.

156
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,000
Thank you.

157
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,200
You go rest.

158
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,840
I'll take the night shift.

159
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,080
It's okay.

160
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,279
I want to stay with Grandpa.

161
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,559
I want him to see me first
when he wakes up.

162
00:08:57,639 --> 00:08:58,320
Alright.

163
00:08:58,919 --> 00:09:00,080
We'll take turns then.

164
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,000
So we won't miss it.

165
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,559
Zechen.

166
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,519
Yeah?

167
00:09:07,919 --> 00:09:09,200
Don't you think

168
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:11,559
Qiao Wenjun acted strange today?

169
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:13,200
How?

170
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:16,279
She just felt different.

171
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,440
She's lost everything

172
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,360
she was holding onto.

173
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,639
Even the person she feared most,

174
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,799
your grandpa, is back.

175
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,960
She has no way
to take over the company now.

176
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,039
No, that's not it.

177
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:37,500
(Duan Yiran)

178
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:43,720
(Duan Yiran)

179
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,039
Hey, Qiao Nian.

180
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,039
I'm not here

181
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:47,360
to start trouble.

182
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,919
I just need to confirm something.

183
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:49,960
What is it?

184
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,600
My mom's acting weird.

185
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:53,639
Please, go check on her.

186
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:00,660
(Inheritance Donation Agreement)

187
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,120
Qiao Wenjun!

188
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:06,759
Qiao Wenjun!

189
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:07,960
Aunt Wenjun!

190
00:10:08,759 --> 00:10:09,559
Aunt Wenjun!

191
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:19,730
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

192
00:10:20,010 --> 00:10:27,610
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

193
00:10:27,660 --> 00:10:31,450
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

194
00:10:31,970 --> 00:10:35,250
♪Where this ends♪

195
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:42,530
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

196
00:10:42,530 --> 00:10:46,860
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

197
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:49,980
♪Love turns into pain♪

198
00:10:50,050 --> 00:10:54,170
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

199
00:10:54,330 --> 00:10:57,810
♪Yet I still want you close♪

200
00:10:57,810 --> 00:11:01,980
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

201
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:05,290
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

202
00:11:05,290 --> 00:11:09,860
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

203
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:16,170
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

204
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:20,950
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

205
